<li id="cite_note-2"><b><a href="#cite_ref-2" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="news">"<a href="http://www.crn.com/networking/214502232" class="external text" title="http://www.crn.com/networking/214502232" rel="nofollow">Proposed Child Pornography Laws Raise Data Retention Concerns</a>". <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Channel_Web&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Channel Web (page does not exist)">Channel Web</a></i>. February 20, 2009<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.crn.com/networking/214502232" class="external free" title="http://www.crn.com/networking/214502232" rel="nofollow">http://www.crn.com/networking/214502232</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2009-03-17</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Proposed+Child+Pornography+Laws+Raise+Data+Retention+Concerns&amp;rft.jtitle=%5B%5BChannel+Web%5D%5D&amp;rft.date=February+20%2C+2009&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.crn.com%2Fnetworking%2F214502232&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Telecommunications_data_retention"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
